<center>
<p><b><font size=+2>Introduction</font></b>
<hr WIDTH="100%"></center>
<font size=+1>Nowadays, E-commerce is a new and rapidly developing area.
Therefore, e-commerce should be investigated using Multimedia Software
Engineering point of view and new MICE tools should be developed for this
area.</font>
<p><font size=+1>How MICE design methodology can be used in e- commerce
environment? As known, most of companies have web sites, and they serve
some services using these pages. Most of these pages need interactive action.
Using CGI programs performs these actions. These programs should be prepared
by using different techniques. MICE environment also can be used to realize
the active systems in e-commerce. In this study, active index system approach
was applied to make reservation and to buy an airline ticket in optimum
price as an example.</font>
